Afro-pop singer Kiss Daniel releases a Valentine’s Day special to his fans with the video to his latest single, ‘4Dayz’. The Video, directed by Sesan was shot in Lagos, Nigeria; it starts with the artist, adorned in beautiful African print, being approached by a guest to sing for a girl at a party. He then goes on to deliver ‘4Dayz’ to the excitement of the couple in his unique style as he sings, “Girl I am loving you ‘4 dayz’,” “Anytime you call my name e be like I dey craze.” The video ends on a romantic note as the couple exit the party together. It is in sync with this season of love and one worth watching.